        },
        {
            "title": "華潤醫藥去年多賺20.7%兼增派息 股價初段曾飆逾10%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">華潤醫藥(03320)今早派2025年度成績，多賺20.7%兼增末期息；該股今早應聲向上，初段最多曾漲逾10%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華潤醫藥官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230831_FI_source-web_03320.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤醫藥官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230831_FI_source-web_03320.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華潤醫藥官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該股今早一度衝上4.91元，飆10.34%；截至上午約10時29分，升幅收窄至9.44%，報4.87元，成交己達1.86億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司今早公布，在2025年度實現公司擁有人應佔溢利40.46億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年升20.7%。淨利潤96.53億元，增長14.9%；總收入2695.74億元，按年也升4.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">董事會擬派末期息每股0.122元，較對上年度同期的0.052元提升1.35倍。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15788108-%e8%8f%af%e6%bd%a4%e9%86%ab%e8%97%a5%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e5%a4%9a%e8%b3%ba20-7%e5%85%bc%e5%a2%9e%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af-%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e6%9b%be%e9%a3%86%e9%80%be10",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/03320.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 10:39:49",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "國際油價急回 傳美尋求與伊朗停火1個月",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">有外媒報道指，美國正尋求與伊朗停火1個月，市場憧憬波斯灣石油出口恢復，油價應聲回吐。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/767a154363f4aed9c8af36966c4f701a_APTOPIX_Israel_Iran_War_51894.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/767a154363f4aed9c8af36966c4f701a_APTOPIX_Israel_Iran_War_51894.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">國際油價急挫，倫敦布蘭特期油一度跌6.3%，低見每桶97.87美元；紐約期油亦跌約5.5%，報每桶87.3美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另一邊廂，避險情緒升温則帶動金價上揚，現貨金一度升2.5%，逼近每盎司4600美元水平，較早時報每盎司4585.1美元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15787958-%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e6%80%a5%e5%9b%9e-%e5%82%b3%e7%be%8e%e5%b0%8b%e6%b1%82%e8%88%87%e4%bc%8a%e6%9c%97%e5%81%9c%e7%81%ab1%e5%80%8b%e6%9c%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20200413-CH-%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E8%BC%B8%E5%87%BA%E5%9C%8B%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94_FB-1-1-1-1-3-1-1-1-2-3-1-1_source-ap_.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-25 10:05:38",
